Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.12,0:02:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\fs42\fad(300,300)}{\move(720,60,720,8)}{\blur3}字幕重校、压制：巴洛克哥特
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.40,0:00:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}多么祥和啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.06,0:00:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}非常一般的乡下吧 什么都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.09,0:00:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}四年没回来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.19,0:00:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有那么久了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.28,0:00:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一次都没有回过故乡么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.89,0:00:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就算回来也没有家人等着啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.79,0:00:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}少佐你也大概听说了我们的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.38,0:00:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.59,0:00:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真难得
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.28,0:00:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}温莉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.43,0:00:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}温莉 我们的常客来了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.40,0:01:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}人没有什么牺牲的话就什么都得不到
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.03,0:01:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为了得到什么东西 就需要付出同等的代价
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.43,0:01:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那就是炼金术的等价交换原则
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.07,0:01:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那时我们坚信那就是世界的真实
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.88,0:03:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fn华康雅艺体W6\pos(720,760)\3c&HD3CF9C&\fs70}有家人在等待的家
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.12,0:03:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你还好吧 丹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.88,0:03:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}皮纳可婆婆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.61,0:03:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好久不见
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.11,0:03:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}又要麻烦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.23,0:03:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.56,0:03:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这次毁得够彻底的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.32,0:03:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是啊 出了不少事情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.28,0:03:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不过你怎么好像变矮了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.81,0:03:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}谁个子矮啊 超微型老太婆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.51,0:03:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}说你呢 豆丁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.51,0:03:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}闭嘴 矮冬瓜老太婆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.73,0:03:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}微型豆丁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.74,0:03:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}微尘老太婆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.53,0:03:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}爱德华·艾尔利克
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.81,0:03:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不管这位是什么样的人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.17,0:03:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就由我阿姆斯特朗来给她点教训吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.76,0:03:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这是哪位
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.38,0:03:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}听不懂玩笑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.68,0:03:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我叫阿莱克斯·鲁伊·阿姆斯特朗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.31,0:03:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我叫皮纳可·洛克威尔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.21,0:03:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.93,0:04:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}臭温莉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.47,0:04:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}想谋杀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.59,0:04:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你才是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.70,0:04:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}搞成那个样子想怎么样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.52,0:04:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真是的 怎么回事嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.15,0:04:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我呕心沥血制成的最高级机械铠
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.93,0:04:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎么可能会被打成碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.29,0:04:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就是那样啦 很轻易就…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.66,0:04:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}阿尔也变得不成样子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.69,0:04:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你们一定干了很危险的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.11,0:04:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.29,0:04:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂 豆丁
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.75,0:04:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}稍微长高了一点嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.70,0:04:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不许叫我豆丁
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.64,0:04:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这样的话 腿也需要调整呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.72,0:04:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}手臂也要从头再做
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.15,0:04:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一周能完成吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.15,0:04:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们有急事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.11,0:04:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不要小看我哟
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.54,0:04:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}三天就好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.38,0:04:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不好意思啦 婆婆
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.51,0:04:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可是 为什么这么急呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.26,0:05:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们要赶快回中央去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.04,0:05:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有很重要的东西要找
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.92,0:05:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不会是很危险的东西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.49,0:05:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.44,0:05:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不是那种东西啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.00,0:05:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真是的 老是给人家添麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.84,0:05:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}温莉虽然嘴巴不饶人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.09,0:05:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但总是会帮我们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.61,0:05:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.01,0:05:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}同是备用品 婆婆做出来的果然就不一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.21,0:05:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不过话说回来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.29,0:05:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这里真是没有变呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.46,0:05:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.90,0:05:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}您叫阿姆斯特朗对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.80,0:05:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那两个孩子 每天都干些什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.22,0:06:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}乡下地方收不到城里的消息
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.62,0:06:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那两个孩子也不写封信来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.93,0:06:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我很担心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.78,0:06:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}艾尔利克兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.96,0:06:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}尤其是钢之炼金术师
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.94,0:06:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在中央逗留了很长时间
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.09,0:06:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因此也被卷入了麻烦之中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.62,0:06:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是都没出什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.07,0:06:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那对兄弟很坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.21,0:06:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}坚强啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.21,0:06:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}救救哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.73,0:06:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}忍一忍
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.78,0:06:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这样的痛楚…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.52,0:06:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}得早点去中央
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.69,0:06:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}查找贤者之石的资料啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.07,0:06:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}虽说如此
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.16,0:06:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}现在就放松放松吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.43,0:06:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}回了那边以后就辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.86,0:06:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.22,0:07:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一直这么发呆可不合我的性格耶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.30,0:07:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.71,0:07:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}去给妈妈扫墓吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.44,0:07:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}扫墓啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.40,0:07:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}机械铠修好了就要马上出发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.64,0:07:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以趁现在去好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.06,0:07:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我就在这里看家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.97,0:07:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是啊 去一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.36,0:07:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}柴劈好了 皮纳可女士
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.82,0:07:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不好意思呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.43,0:07:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你也好好休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.35,0:07:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.25,0:07:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}作为军人每天都不能欠缺锻炼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.10,0:07:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}说起来 爱德华不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.25,0:07:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}说是给母亲扫墓去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.84,0:07:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}明明跟他说过一个人出去很危险的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.63,0:08:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.47,0:08:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有个优秀的保镖跟着
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.94,0:08:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}爱德 回来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.59,0:08:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是啊 好久不见
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.58,0:08:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有四五年没见了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.08,0:08:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不过还是这么矮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.94,0:08:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不准说我矮
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.05,0:08:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你还在当那个国家什么的么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.49,0:08:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.56,0:08:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}保重身体啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.32,0:08:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因为你个子矮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.71,0:08:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不准说个子矮
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.83,0:08:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎么了 发什么呆呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.46,0:08:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}温莉 那个女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.55,0:08:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是内琳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.70,0:08:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}小的时候经常在一起玩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.28,0:08:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}捉迷藏啦 去河边玩啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.46,0:09:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.25,0:09:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}已经不记得她的样子了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.75,0:09:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是啊 女大十八变呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.19,0:09:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.66,0:09:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}阿尔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.56,0:09:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}把妈妈恢复原样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.48,0:09:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们回去吧 丹
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.60,0:09:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这就是那个怀表?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.19,0:10:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}使炼成阵的能力增幅的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.18,0:10:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.92,0:10:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}做工这么精细 装饰也那么精美
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.29,0:10:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不愧是名匠的作品
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.25,0:10:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}内部构造是怎么样的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.45,0:10:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}机械的还是自动的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.86,0:10:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}莫非是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.36,0:10:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}行了 没什么特别的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.14,0:10:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}求你了 就让我研究研究
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.88,0:10:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}别开玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.81,0:10:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}交给你的话 会连最后一颗螺丝都给拆掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.50,0:10:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有什么不好的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.75,0:10:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就算拆开我也能给你装回去的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.17,0:10:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.76,0:10:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.52,0:10:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你找别人去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.63,0:10:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好了 请让我去劈一年份的柴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.70,0:10:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什么嘛 小气
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.79,0:10:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}阿尔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.48,0:10:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}照婆婆说的 明天胳膊就能做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.55,0:10:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}然后首先就是要把你修好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.02,0:11:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哥哥 我有朋友吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.95,0:11:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎么突然问这个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.22,0:11:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不知怎么的记忆很模糊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.72,0:11:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}朋友的长相也记不起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.21,0:11:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}记忆这种东西就是一点一点增加的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.50,0:11:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}会忘记过去的事也是很自然啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.49,0:11:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是这样么…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.62,0:11:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂 阿尔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.69,0:11:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有些话虽然一直想对你说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.58,0:11:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但因为很害怕 所以一直没说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.28,0:11:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.66,0:11:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.13,0:11:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.85,0:11:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不 还是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.04,0:11:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.53,0:12:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}少年们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.45,0:12:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}看吧 那美丽的夜空
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.31,0:12:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那满天的星光
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.85,0:12:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那是在城市里无法看到的上天的恩赐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.25,0:12:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}利森普尔这村子 真是个好地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.14,0:12:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}虽说缺少很多东西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.28,0:12:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但反过来也有很多都市里没有的东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.13,0:12:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}以前 我们也经常这样仰望星空呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.64,0:12:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好了 久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.27,0:12:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是时候接驳了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.18,0:12:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}虽然不是第一次了 不过连接神经那瞬间啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.11,0:12:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}别像个小孩子似的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.93,0:12:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}还想快点回中央去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.96,0:12:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那还用你说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.37,0:12:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要早点恢复原来的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.32,0:12:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}告别现在这种痛苦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.59,0:12:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那真可惜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.95,0:12:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}本来还指望靠你赚钱的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.76,0:12:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}对呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.68,0:13:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}别硬是要恢复原来的身体啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.23,0:13:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}机油的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.32,0:13:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}咯吱咯吱作响的人造肌肉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.06,0:13:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}低吟的轴承
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.95,0:13:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}机械铠真是太好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.64,0:13:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}机械狂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.82,0:13:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什么嘛 炼金狂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.63,0:13:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那么 开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.67,0:13:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.56,0:13:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}二
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.45,0:13:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}三
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.24,0:13:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你们两个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.41,0:13:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}爱德要睡在那里 让个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.48,0:13:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没想到接驳的时候居然会那么疼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.38,0:13:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}连成年人也会忍不住大叫出来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.50,0:13:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可不一般啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.33,0:13:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.32,0:13:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这次的钢材跟上次比起来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.90,0:13:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}重量只有80%
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.97,0:13:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}太重的话会让你长不高的 那就不妙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.75,0:13:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你这家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.79,0:13:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}别人还痛苦着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.48,0:13:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你就别提个子的事了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.44,0:14:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你这么有精神 没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.35,0:14:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没什么不舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.31,0:14:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因为减轻了重量
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.48,0:14:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以硬度稍微下降了些
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.35,0:14:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一定不要太乱来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.57,0:14:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}机械铠是可以再换
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.44,0:14:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}命可是只有一条啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.07,0:14:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我也一宿没睡 累死了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.34,0:14:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}多谢你 温莉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.82,0:14:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}加急费用可不低哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.16,0:14:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}阿尔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.45,0:14:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}已经没问题了吧 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.33,0:14:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}完全没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.01,0:14:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.41,0:14:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}现在就来把你修好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.49,0:14:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}盔甲的碎片就这么些吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.39,0:14:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是少佐他们小心翼翼收集起来的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.77,0:14:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}马上就能修好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.00,0:14:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}稍微要点窍门呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.90,0:14:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这里有一个印记吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.08,0:15:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这就是连接阿尔的灵魂和盔甲的媒介
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.91,0:15:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真是危险的地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.02,0:15:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要是画得更深一些就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.59,0:15:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不管发生什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.72,0:15:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}都一定要死守着它啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.80,0:15:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因为是把阿尔与盔甲相连的要害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.14,0:15:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好像是用血写的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.03,0:15:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没错 是我的血
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.48,0:15:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}意识模糊时写的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.59,0:15:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.67,0:15:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}多么感人的兄弟感情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.08,0:15:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好伟大的的羁绊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.20,0:15:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你能不能闪开
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.45,0:15:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}别在那里碍事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.99,0:15:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.80,0:15:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}感觉真好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.49,0:15:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}谢谢哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.84,0:15:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}太好了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.08,0:15:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那么 就像往常一样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.12,0:15:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}像往常一样?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.35,0:15:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.87,0:15:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们的师父说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.53,0:15:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}"要想锻炼精神 首先要锻炼肉体"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.47,0:16:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以平常总是和阿尔练习啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.74,0:16:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可是 我还一次都没有赢过呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.49,0:16:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那么也请让我来帮你们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.45,0:16:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不用客气了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.93,0:16:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好了 上喽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.07,0:16:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我说 胡来的话又会搞坏的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.56,0:16:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.95,0:16:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那么沉迷 还真是个小孩子耶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.92,0:16:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}接下来是我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.03,0:17:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}果然定做的东西就是不一样诶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.38,0:17:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这洗练的浮雕不错
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.79,0:17:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}精美的做工也不错
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.97,0:17:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}里面一定也很厉害吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.09,0:17:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好想看啊 好想拆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.62,0:17:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好想再装配起来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.64,0:17:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}爱德?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.33,0:17:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}看招
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.94,0:17:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}太天真了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.86,0:17:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只有这种水平是无法前进的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.68,0:17:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.91,0:17:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.74,0:17:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.81,0:17:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎么了 到此为止了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.97,0:18:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.18,0:18:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.25,0:18:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}温莉?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.45,0:18:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.30,0:18:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}对不起 我不小心看了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.80,0:18:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你这家伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.99,0:18:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}对不起 实在对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.04,0:18:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.48,0:18:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}连阿尔我都没给他看过
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.08,0:19:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.46,0:19:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我真是软弱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.90,0:19:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不得不这样 把对自己的告诫和决心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.21,0:19:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}付诸于实物 带在身上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.60,0:19:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}爱德
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.77,0:19:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}即使如此 我们既没有亲人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.00,0:19:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也没有能回去的家
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.32,0:19:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只能向前进
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.06,0:19:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为什么 为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.55,0:19:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你们不是有家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.22,0:19:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不是有婆婆和我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.17,0:19:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真是笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.73,0:19:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你干嘛要哭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.96,0:19:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因为你们兄弟俩不哭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.79,0:19:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以我就来替你们哭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.33,0:19:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}爱德他们去哪儿了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.01,0:19:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}别担心 过一阵就会回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.73,0:20:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就像平常一样 等着他们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.13,0:20:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这里是门厅
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.07,0:20:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}然后是起居室
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.28,0:20:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}天冷的时候给火炉加柴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.62,0:20:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哥哥总是偷懒不去劈柴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.53,0:20:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们回家晚了的话 妈妈就会在二楼的窗户点灯 一闪一闪的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.95,0:20:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}灯很亮 不管在哪儿玩 看到那灯光都能马上跑回家
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.01,0:20:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}说起来…确实是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.23,0:20:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你们两个 不是有家嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.16,0:20:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有家人在等待的温暖的家
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.77,0:21:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.21,0:21:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}看
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.68,0:21:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}小子们 偶尔也回来吃个饭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.91,0:21:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好 有时间一定
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.30,0:21:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}婆婆 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.58,0:21:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}托您照顾了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.69,0:21:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.09,0:21:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.86,0:22:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}婆婆
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.68,0:22:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我看到了 在爱德的怀表里
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.60,0:22:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}上面刻着
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.85,0:22:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}两人把房子烧掉 踏上旅途
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.20,0:22:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那天的日期
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.91,0:23:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}钢之炼金术师
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.71,0:23:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}第十八集
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.46,0:23:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}马尔科手记
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.63,0:23:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}中央图书馆 第一分馆
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.77,0:23:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在焚烧后的余烬里
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.89,0:23:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}些微的真实复苏了
